I"<p>之前介绍过用<a href="/python/2019/05/13/anaconda.html" title="/python/2019/05/13/anaconda.html">anaconda</a>创建python的虚拟环境，本贴记录如何在<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vscode</code>和<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pycharm</code>编辑器中切换<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">anaconda</code>创建的虚拟环境</p>

<h1 id="1vscode切换虚拟环境">1.vscode切换虚拟环境</h1>

<p>打开<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vscode</code>编辑器，按下<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ctrl + shift + p</code>，在命令面板输入</p>

<pre><code class="language-txt">python: select interpreter
</code></pre>

<p>输入完成后，会出现已有的虚拟环境，选择想要切换的环境</p>

<p><img src="http://walidream.com:9999/blogImage/python/python_32.png" alt="ssl" /></p>

<h1 id="2pycharm切换虚拟环境">2.pycharm切换虚拟环境</h1>

<p>打开<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pycharm</code>编辑器，选择<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">file</code> - &gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">settings</code></p>

<p><img src="http://walidream.com:9999/blogImage/python/python_33.png" alt="ssl" /></p>

<p><img src="http://walidream.com:9999/blogImage/python/python_34.png" alt="ssl" /></p>

<p><img src="http://walidream.com:9999/blogImage/python/python_52.png" alt="ssl" /></p>

<p>选择<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Existing environment</code> -&gt; <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">interpreter</code>，添加自己想要的虚拟环境。</p>

